snippet.title: Meet Sirfetch’d in Pokémon Sword! ⚔️
snippet.description:
🚨 New Pokémon Discovered! 🚨

Meet Sirfetch’d, the Wild Duck Pokémon! Farfetch’d that inhabit the Galar region can evolve into Sirfetch’d after experiencing many battles. http://bit.ly/2kny0uq

Leave a ⚔️ below if you’re ready to learn more about this Pokémon!
